urls.title: Reopening | San Francisco
urls.description: Guidance, updates, and resources on how San Francisco is reopening during the coronavirus pandemic.

text:
San Franciscans took our Stay Home order seriously, and as a result we flattened the curve and prevented a widespread COVID-19 outbreak.

Here's our timeline and plan for how we're going to gradually reopen, using data and additional safety precautions: https://t.co/ZiNNIWQEmU
